  "texts": [
    "This rapid processing capability significantly elevates MobileNet above other models in terms of efficiency.",
    "To illustrate this, consider the comparison with models such as regions with CNN features (R-CNN) and its enhanced version, Fast R-CNN.",
    "While these models exhibit higher accuracy rates, capturing more detailed information than MobileNet, they lag in processing speed.",
    "The defining advantage of MobileNet lies in its speed, making it a preferred option for applications where prompt and efficient object detection is crucial.",
    "This aspect is particularly vital in real-world scenarios where time-sensitive detection is paramount [32]."
  ],
